Search files
    locate
    updatedb - this updates the db
    find / -name test.txt

Search in files
    grep
    grep -i 
    grep -r text <directory>
    grep -v
    grep -w exam  exmaples.txt (match the whole word)
    grep -vw
    grep -A1 text <file> - one line next matching the pattern
    grep -B1 text <file> - one line before matching the pattern
    grep -A1 -B1 text <file> - one line before and after
      